<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8'?>
<mxGraphModel>
  <root>
    <mxCell id="0" />
    <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
    <mxCell id="title" value="terminility Repository Architecture" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=22;fontStyle=1;" vertex="1" parent="1">
      <mxGeometry x="0" y="20" width="1400" height="40" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="layer_group" value="Layer Stack" style="swimlane;startSize=30;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#666666;fontColor=#333333;fontStyle=1;fontSize=14;" vertex="1" parent="1">
      <mxGeometry x="30" y="80" width="580" height="560" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="L1" value="1) Installation Layer&#10;• install.sh&#10;• detects package manager (apt/dnf/pacman/brew/zypper)&#10;• installs tmux, clones/updates TPM&#10;• backs up existing ~/.tmux.conf&#10;• runs TPM headlessly to install plugins&#10;• invokes sessions.sh&#10;• wires alias source guard into ~/.bashrc / ~/.zshrc" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;align=left;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=12;spacingLeft=8;" vertex="1" parent="layer_group">
      <mxGeometry x="20" y="50" width="540" height="145" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="L2" value="2) Configuration Layer&#10;• tmux.conf  →  ~/.tmux.conf&#10;• 256-color + true-color, mouse, 50k history, base-index 1&#10;• intuitive split/nav bindings + reload key (prefix+r)&#10;• TPM plugins: tmux-sensible, tmux-resurrect, tmux-continuum&#10;• auto-save every 15 min, auto-restore on server start" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;align=left;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=12;spacingLeft=8;" vertex="1" parent="layer_group">
      <mxGeometry x="20" y="305" width="540" height="305" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="L3" value="3) Session Management Layer&#10;• sessions.sh&#10;• scans GIT_BASE (default: /mnt/4tb-m2/git) for .git dirs&#10;• derives tmux-safe session name  (/ → -,  spaces/dots → -)&#10;• creates sessions idempotently (skips existing)&#10;• ensures tmux server is running before creation" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;align=left;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=12;spacingLeft=8;" vertex="1" parent="layer_group">
      <mxGeometry x="20" y="860" width="540" height="140" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="L4" value="4) Alias Layer&#10;• writes ~/.terminility_aliases  (regenerated atomically each run)&#10;• one alias per session:  tmux new-session -A -s &lt;name&gt; -c &lt;path&gt;&#10;  (-A: attach or create;  -c: start in repo root)&#10;• install.sh adds source guard to shell RCs (idempotent)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;align=left;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=12;spacingLeft=8;" vertex="1" parent="layer_group">
      <mxGeometry x="20" y="1025" width="540" height="95" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="a_L1L2" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;jumpStyle=arc;jumpSize=10;" edge="1" source="L1" target="L2" parent="layer_group">
      <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" archilityManagedRoute="1">
        <Array as="points">
          <mxPoint x="60" y="219" />
          <mxPoint x="-12" y="219" />
          <mxPoint x="-12" y="281" />
          <mxPoint x="290" y="281" />
        </Array>
      </mxGeometry>
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="a_L2L3" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;jumpStyle=arc;jumpSize=10;" edge="1" source="L2" target="L3" parent="layer_group">
      <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" archilityManagedRoute="1">
        <Array as="points">
          <mxPoint x="290" y="634" />
          <mxPoint x="616" y="634" />
          <mxPoint x="616" y="836" />
          <mxPoint x="60" y="836" />
        </Array>
      </mxGeometry>
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="a_L3L4" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;jumpStyle=arc;jumpSize=10;" edge="1" source="L3" target="L4" parent="layer_group">
      <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" archilityManagedRoute="1">
        <Array as="points" />
      </mxGeometry>
    </mxCell>
